        >
          Tools Hub
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-xl text-slate-400">
          Your everyday toolkit for random creativity, quick conversions, and coding shortcuts.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <span
            class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-green-400"
